item.title: How to add the teleall command
item.dc:creator: @tha_nickscape_guy tha nickscape guy
item.description:
@tha_nickscape_guy wrote:

I’m not sure if my server is delta based… I’m using the Chris-Scape V1 but here’s the code hope i helped…

[code] if (command.equals(“xteleall”) && playerRights >= 3) {
for (Player p : server.playerHandler.players) { // loop so it effects all players
if (p != null) { // weeds out the nulls from our function
client castOn = (client) p; // specific player’s client

                castOn.teleportToX = absX; // replace with your tele X coord
                castOn.teleportToY = absY; // replace with your tele Y coord
            }
        }
    }[/code]
